text: Tan Min (; born 25 August 1972) is a former synchronized swimmer from China. She competed in both the 1988 and 1992 Summer Olympics. == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of China Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Synchronized swimmers from Chongqing Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 1991 World Aquatics Championships
